    public class WfJsonMessage
extends com.github.cliftonlabs.json_simple.JsonObject
    Whiteflag JSON message representation

    This obejct represents a Whiteflag message represented in the JavaScript Object Notation (JSON) format, in accordance with Annex B of the Whiteflag specification. The basic structure is as follows: { "MetaHeader" : {}, "MessageHeader": {}, "MessageBody": {} }
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
